description: Buddha Bruddah's amazing selection of Asian mixed plates will change the way you think about lunch! Would you like the pad thai? Red Curry? Asian slaw? How about all of those on one plate, with 2 scoops of rice and more flavor than you can shake a stick at! Never again limit yourself to just a burger, hot dog, or burrito. Go experience the taste sensations available at Buddha Bruddah!
name: Buddha Bruddah
